text: Mister International Azerbaijan (Mister International Azerbaycan) is a national male beauty pageant in Azerbaijan. The grand winner will represent the country at the Mister International pageant. This pageant unrelated to Miss Azerbaijan or Mister Azerbaijan. ==Pageant== The Mister International Azerbaijan has been independent pageant since 2014. It is in under Zamir Hüseynov management in Baku, Azerbaijan.
